{
  "texts": [
    "During inference, the most likely action is chosen greedily.",
    "The state vector forming the input of the layout planner policy network is also passed to the value network.",
    "A two-layer fully connected NN approximates the value function.",
    "The scheduling agent solves the completely reactive online FJSP.",
    "Thus, the agent computes only the next station and process step pairing for each job."
  ]
}